{"tid":928191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"起初我以為只有新界北學生會咁...","createTime":"2018-12-04T15:55:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T02:28:24.000Z","uid":137335,"like":847,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"0d87dc1c226a21a78e4cbd89cc45bf2e9eeb7e87","tid":928191,"uid":137335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T15:55:31.000Z","msg":"眾所鳩知，新界北嘅學生一早變成深圳人為主，蝗語為主。為咗埋堆，我地本地嘅學生都因為咁同果班小蝗子用蝗語溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n          但今日我因公事，要係學生嘅放學時間落荃灣一轉，搭嘅車路經荃灣，有班學生上車<br />\n<br />\n佢！<br />\n地！<br />\n全！<br />\n撚！<br />\n部！<br />\n講！<br />\n蝗！<br />\n語！<br />\n<br />\n         跟住我去咗沙咀道果間M記醫肚，入面啲staff佢地溝通係蝗語，唔係單指後生果班，年紀大啲，中年，全撚部都係<br />\n<br />\n          準確啲係成間舖都充訴蝗語，staff講，學生又講，啲阿伯又講<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母呢到香港黎架<br />\n<br />\n我心灰，唔係因為香港變成咁<br />\n<br />\n而係我眼白白見到香港變成咁<br />\n<br />\n我唔知可以做咩，於是我上黎連登出post<br />\n<br />\n我唔想有一日，我住嘅香港只會變成一個只係叫香港嘅地方"},{"pid":"75d117132363ab1fe2404f3ef5cdb29ca59121c1","tid":928191,"uid":5793,"like":323,"dislike":5,"score":318,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T16:21:00.000Z","msg":"日經⋯<br />\n呢樣野發生左好多年啦<br />\n種族大清洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4c6eebe0eb873c9494d2cf2fe793da7368c428","tid":928191,"uid":139700,"like":209,"dislike":6,"score":203,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T16:26:40.000Z","msg":"啲泛民ON9支持者快撚啲死啦，錢又唔係你哋袋，選班垃圾議員，好似11哥徒弟咁，總辭啦仆街"},{"pid":"58c0d9029d7295f47dc6f1afdf124f7e26b7c65d","tid":928191,"uid":30836,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T16:31:32.000Z","msg":"樓下啲保安都係<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/smile_39.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_39.gif&h=1139c508&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f34073b8b45273a5e5006d9d257cf102a9a58e38","tid":928191,"uid":79563,"like":205,"dislike":3,"score":202,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"